            "title": "蔚來曾挫逾8%   折讓近9.5%配股",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">蔚來(09866)今早最多挫8.14%，見29.9元，現跌7.37%，報30.15元。成交3.93億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240603_FI_source-web_09866-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240603_FI_source-web_09866-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：蔚來官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集團公布作價每股29.46元配售股份，較昨日收市價32.55元折讓9.49%，配售最多近1.368億股A類普通股股份，配售集資最多40.3億元。</p>\n</div>",
