            "title": "港股開升94點   內險及運動服股向好 蔚來挫近半成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數開報23672，升94點或0.4% ; 恒生國企指數開報8709升31點或0.37% ; 恒生科技指數開報5605點，升16點或0.29%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"蔚來官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-184615__source-web_09866_NIO_source-web__704px-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"蔚來官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-184615__source-web_09866_NIO_source-web__704px-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">蔚來官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交 25.25億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">蔚來(09866)折讓9.49%，作價29.46元配股集逾40億元，股價開跌4.15%，報31.2元木</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">小米(01810)跌1.35%，報51元，成交居第二位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">京東(09618)升2.07%，報168元 ;騰訊(00700)升0.49%，報511.5元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新華保險(01336)揚5.45%，報30元，集團新業務價值增106.78%，純利增201.1%，派息增134.12%至1.99元。平保(023189)也升1.27%，報47.8元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">李寧(02331)升3.51%，報17.7元，末期息增12%至20.73分 ; 安踏(02020)升1.29%，報90.65元。</p>\n</div>",
